808
00:45:32,686 --> 00:45:34,209
What do you mean?

809
00:45:34,253 --> 00:45:36,995
Well, I was in a café last week,

810
00:45:37,038 --> 00:45:39,084
and I overheard his wife Rita

811
00:45:39,127 --> 00:45:41,477
