00:45:54,490 --> 00:45:56,492
Maybe it's wrong of me,
but I felt that I had

818
00:45:56,536 --> 00:45:57,755
to say something.

819
00:45:57,798 --> 00:45:59,669
No.

820
00:45:59,713 --> 00:46:01,846
